lines: In the midst of training I was, my body aflame, my garments soaked through with sweat, when these kindred spirits begged leave to train together! You are welcome to join us too, my friend!
Today is the day for which we have trained body and mind with passion and vigor! We will not fail─Doma will be free!
The rebuilding of our homeland will be no less demanding than our efforts to reclaim it. We will need to train our bodies to their physical peaks! Daily and no less rigorously than before!
Fear not, my ladylord. Should Yotsuyu attempt to escape, these finely honed muscles will stop her dead in her tracks.
The Empire promises peace with Doma, but I will not let down my guard, nor will I slacken my training. Come what may, I will be ready.
Master Gosetsu will not return to find us soft and sagging, oh no! Constant training and iron discipline for these warriors!

レインボークロス・スカウトシャツ
